 in public to ward off coronavirus has shifted. First they were deemed unhelpful, but experts and leaders now insist on their use. In the Daily Beast, Katie McBride provides some welcome clarity with the science of airborne transmission. For me, it affirms the choice to maintain physical distancing but not don a cloth while out running.</p></details></div><div class="_528b6" itemProp="about" itemscope="" itemType="https://schema.org/NewsArticle"><a class="_12036" href="/co/2978516/your-mask-may-not-be-enough-if-covid-19-is-in-the-air/"><div class="_58631" itemProp="image" itemscope="" itemType="https://schema.org/imageObject"><div class="_2e8cc a1afd visible" style="padding-bottom:100%"><img src="https://i0.wp.com/qz-news.imgix.net/2978516/thumbnail?auto=compress" srcSet="https://i0.wp.com/qz-news.imgix.net/2978516/thumbnail?auto=compress&amp;w=150&amp;h=150&amp;crop=1&amp;strip=all&amp;quality=75 150w, https://i0.wp.com/qz-news.imgix.net/2978516/thumbnail?auto=compress&amp;w=200&amp;h=200&amp;crop=1&amp;strip=all&amp;quality=75 200w" sizes="(max-width: 26.5624em) 150px, (min-width: 48em) 200px, 200px" alt="" class="" decoding="async"/></div><meta itemProp="url" content="https://i0.wp.com/qz-news.imgix.net/2978516/thumbnail?auto=compress"/></div><div class="_71aea"><h3 itemProp="headline" class="_095bb">Your Mask May Not Be Enough if COVID-19 Is in the Air</h3><div class="b42b5"><span itemProp="publisher">The Daily Beast</span><time itemProp="datePublished" class="date" dateTime="2020-04-17T18:46:27.600Z">April 17, 2020</time></div></div></a></div></div><div class="b17d7"><div class="a7009" id="pick-footer-2978516"><div class="_8104f"><button aria-label="Like contribution (liked 1 times)" aria-pressed="false" class="_58140"><span aria-hidden="true" class="_3fea6">💡</span><span class="_79cad">Made me smarter</span><span class="e4bcb _87de4">1</span></button></div><time class="_53bd2" dateTime="2020-04-17T19:26:07.735Z">April 17, 2020</time></div></div></div></div><di