ps://schema.org/text"><summary class="_73aa5"><p>Hearing about loss of smell and/or taste more and more as a symptom of Covid-19. If you experience this phenomenon, you may want to consider it an early-warning sign, especially if you don't have immediate access to medical care or testing. Remember to follow medical recommendations for at-home treatment</p></summary><p>Hearing about loss of smell and/or taste more and more as a symptom of Covid-19. If you experience this phenomenon, you may want to consider it an early-warning sign, especially if you don't have immediate access to medical care or testing. Remember to follow medical recommendations for at-home treatment and to self-isolate, as the CDC, WHO, and other medical authorities direct.</p></details></div><div class="_528b6" itemProp="about" itemscope="" itemType="https://schema.org/NewsArticle"><a class="_12036" href="/co/2965778/the-loss-of-taste-and-smell-are-possible-symptoms-of-covid-19/"><div class="_58631" itemProp="image" itemscope="" itemType="https://schema.org/imageObject"><div class="_2e8cc a1afd visible" style="padding-bottom:100%"><img src="https://i0.wp.com/qz-news.imgix.net/2965778/thumbnail?auto=compress" srcSet="https://i0.wp.com/qz-news.imgix.net/2965778/thumbnail?auto=compress&amp;w=150&amp;h=150&amp;crop=1&amp;strip=all&amp;quality=75 150w, https://i0.wp.com/qz-news.imgix.net/2965778/thumbnail?auto=compress&amp;w=200&amp;h=200&amp;crop=1&amp;strip=all&amp;quality=75 200w" sizes="(max-width: 26.5624em) 150px, (min-width: 48em) 200px, 200px" alt="" class="" decoding="async"/></div><meta itemProp="url" content="https://i0.wp.com/qz-news.imgix.net/2965778/thumbnail?auto=compress"/></div><div class="_71aea"><h3 itemProp="headline" class="_095bb">The loss of taste and smell are possible symptoms of Covid-19</h3><div class="b42b5"><span itemProp="publisher">Quartz</span><time itemProp="datePublished" class="date" dateTime="2020-03-23T21:19:00.975Z">March 23, 2020</time></div></div></a></div></div